WHEREAS, the Assessor/Expert represents that s(he) is technically knowledgeable
and experienced in assessing the competence of a CABs;

WHEREAS, NINAS operates a national program to assess and accredit laboratories utilizing
the services of skilled independent contractor Assessor/Expert;

WHEREAS, NINAS seeks to engage the Assessor/Expert to provide such services, and;

WHEREAS, the Assessor/Expert is available and wishes to perform such tasks;

NOW THEREFORE, it is mutually agreed by and between the parties hereto as follows:

p.strong:
Services: The Assessor/Expert agrees to provide the following services to NINAS:
a) Assessments using reference documents supplied by NINAS, based on NINAS designated national and international standards for accreditation, and using the Assessor/Expert's knowledge of particular specific areas of assessment;
b) Written reports of the assessments and of the Non conformities found in the assessment against the accreditation requirements including the details of an applicant's Scope of Accreditation, as applicable;
c) Perform in a professional manner the duties and responsibilities of NINAS Assessor/Expert within the limits prescribed by NINAS.
